Various Otyebis Crew:




Dragoon's transmission was received by one of the many antennaes and was 
processed.  Scans reported that the transmission had been reported from a 
base that, according to the bounty hunters, belonged to a faction called the 
Destrons ruled by Magmatron.  But they wanted to be sure.

A reply transmission was sent.  "Thank you, Dragoon, for entering the IGL's 
Regular League.  We still need to know if you are in a faction, and if so 
what is it called.  Thank you again."
